{"name": "gptstonks-multiagents", "metadata": {"name": "gptstonks-multiagents", "version": "0.0.2", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["gptstonks-wrappers", "langgraph", "langchain", "asyncio", "llama-index", "duckduckgo-search", "wikipedia", "llama-index-llms-openai", "langchain-community"], "summary": "Multi-Agent architectures to create copilots and autopilots.", "upload_time": 1733833791}, "documentation": ["<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"../../docs/assets/logo-chatbot.png\" alt=\"Logo\">\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <!-- Waitlist Badge -->\n  <a href=\"https://gptstonks.net/login\"><img src=\"../../docs/assets/waitlist_badge.png\" alt=\"Join Waitlist Badge\"></a>\n  <!-- YT Badge -->\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@GPTStonks\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/channel-ff0000?style=for-the-badge&logo=youtube&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Youtube Channel Badge\"></a>\n  <!-- X Badge -->\n  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/GPTStonks\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/follow_us-000000?style=for-the-badge&logo=x&logoColor=white\" alt=\"X Follow Us Badge\"></a>\n  <!-- Discord Badge -->\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/MyDDGuEd\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Discord-5865F2?style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord Badge\"></a>\n  <!-- Docker Badge -->\n  <a href=\"https://hub.docker.com/u/gptstonks\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Docker-2496ED?style=for-the-badge&logo=docker&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Docker Badge\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <!-- LlamaIndex Badge -->\n  <a href=\"https://www.llamaindex.ai/\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/LlamaIndex-ac6aff?style=for-the-badge&logo=llamaindex&logoColor=white\" alt=\"LlamaIndex Badge\"></a>\n  <!-- LangChain Badge -->\n  <a href=\"https://langchain.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/LangChain-005A9C?style=for-the-badge&logo=langchain&logoColor=white\" alt=\"LangChain Badge\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n# GPTStonks Multi-Agents\n\n## Description\n\nGPTStonks Multi-Agents provides common multi-agent architectures to create copilots and autopilots that solve complex tasks.\n\n## Development\n\n  1. Install [PDM](https://pdm.fming.dev/latest/#installation).\n\n  2. Clone the project and install necessary packages:\n```bash\n# clone project\ngit clone https://github.com/GPTStonks/gptstonks.git\ncd gptstonks\n\n# install pdm\npip install pdm\n\n# install package\npdm install -dG default\n```\n\n## Usage guide\n\nIn the notebook [Multi-Agent With Tools](notebooks/multiagent_with_tools.ipynb) we showcase how multi-agents can be used for advanced knowledge gathering among other tasks. In this particular case to answer music-related questions and make recommendations.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "gptstonks.multiagents.graphs", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "gptstonks.multiagents.graphs.GraphAgentWithTools", "xref": {"fqname": "gptstonks.multiagents.graphs.agent_with_tools.GraphAgentWithTools", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "gptstonks.multiagents", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "gptstonks.multiagents.states", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "gptstonks.multiagents.states.BaseAgentState", "xref": {"fqname": "gptstonks.multiagents.states.base.BaseAgentState", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "gptstonks.multiagents.graphs.agent_with_tools", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "gptstonks.multiagents.graphs.agent_with_tools.GraphAgentWithTools", "bases": ["BaseModel"], "methods": [{"name": "gptstonks.multiagents.graphs.agent_with_tools.GraphAgentWithTools.tool_executor", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name